Pre-Game Insights: England have been dealt an injury blow ahead of Thursday night's UEFA Nations League clash with Greece at Wembley.
Harry Kane is a doubt to feature in Thursday's clash with table-topping Greece due to a thigh issue.
Lee Carsley might need to come up with an alternative solution up front on Thursday if Kane is unavailable.
If fully fit, Kane is a guaranteed starter for England, regardless of often-disrespectful criticism that the forward received during Euro 2024.
